text.tspan: In an assessment of the durability of brick pavers, a sharpened drill impacted the surface
of 10 pavers for a period of 1 minute.
The volume of material eroded (mL) is recorded.
What is the mean hardness of the pavers?
We are 95% confident that the mean hardness
of the pavers is between 286.0 and 302.6.
